Lori A. Schechter
Executive Vice President, General Counsel and Chief Compliance Officer, McKesson Corporation






Lori A. Schechter is executive vice president, general counsel and chief compliance officer for McKesson Corporation. She is responsible for overseeing McKesson‚Äôs general counsel organization, which consists of the law, public affairs, compliance and corporate secretarial functions for McKesson and its subsidiaries.
